%% Data Flow Diagram: Text Generation Inference Server (TGIS)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as TGIS Router<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant Tokenizer as Tokenizer<br/>(in-process Rust)
    participant Shard0 as Server Shard 0<br/>UDS gRPC<br/>plaintext
    participant GPU as GPU<br/>(PyTorch/CUDA)
    participant ShardN as Server Shard 1..N<br/>(NCCL 29500/TCP)

    Note over Client,ShardN: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation (Generate)

    Client->>Router: gRPC Generate(BatchedGenerationRequest)<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Tokenizer: Tokenize input text
    Tokenizer-->>Router: Token IDs + validation
    Router->>Shard0: gRPC Prefill(Batch)<br/>UDS plaintext
    Shard0->>GPU: PyTorch forward pass (CUDA)
    GPU-->>Shard0: First token + KV cache
    loop NextToken until stop condition
        Router->>Shard0: gRPC NextToken(CachedBatch)<br/>UDS plaintext
        Shard0->>GPU: Autoregressive decode
        GPU-->>Shard0: Next token
        Shard0-->>Router: GeneratedText (token)
    end
    Router-->>Client: BatchedGenerationResponse<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS

    Note over Client,ShardN: Flow 2: Streaming Text Generation (GenerateStream)

    Client->>Router: gRPC GenerateStream(SingleGenerationRequest)<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Shard0: gRPC Prefill(Batch)<br/>UDS plaintext
    Shard0->>GPU: PyTorch forward pass (CUDA)
    GPU-->>Shard0: First token
    Shard0-->>Router: Token
    Router-->>Client: StreamResponse (token 1)
    loop Streaming tokens
        Router->>Shard0: gRPC NextToken(CachedBatch)
        Shard0->>GPU: Autoregressive decode
        GPU-->>Shard0: Next token
        Shard0-->>Router: Token
        Router-->>Client: StreamResponse (token N)
    end

    Note over Client,ShardN: Flow 3: Multi-GPU Tensor Parallel Inference

    Router->>Shard0: gRPC Prefill(Batch)<br/>UDS plaintext
    Shard0->>ShardN: NCCL AllReduce<br/>29500/TCP plaintext
    ShardN-->>Shard0: Tensor sync
    Shard0-->>Router: Result (from master shard)
